NFTModule.name: NFTModule
NFTModule.remarks: This module provides ERC721 functionality. It is used to mint 1 of 1 NFTs.

methods.name: getAll
methods.summary: Fetch all NFTs that are contained by the module

examples.javascript:
const module = sdk.getNFTModule("{{module_address}}");
const nfts = await module.getAll();

NFTModule.signature: export declare class NFTModule extends ModuleWithRoles<SignatureMint721> implements ITransferable, ISignatureMinter
